These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Music-Genre: r&b, ambient, gospel
1. Music-Genre:ambient is on the right of Music-Genre:gospel##1
2. Music-Genre:r&b is on the far right##1
3. Music-Genre:r&b is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | ambient | r&b |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Flower: rose, daffodil, poppy
1. Flower:daffodil is in an odd position##4
2. Flower:rose is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Flower   | rose | poppy | daffodil |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Sport: handball, skiing, cricket
1. Sport:skiing is in an even position##4
2. Sport:skiing is on the left or right of Sport:cricket##3
3. Sport:cricket is on the right of Sport:skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Sport   | handball | skiing | cricket |

 #################################
 
